# Architecture

The following image shows the architecture and components of an Edge System.

<Mayflower architecture.png>

### Edge System architecture

Edge System contains the following components:

* Edge Connectivity
    Includes Modbus TCP and OPC UA connectivity. 
* Edge Data Store (EDS)
    EDS includes the following components: OMF endpoint, data storage, API, and data egress. 

Third-party applications that read from or write data to Edge System must reside on the same device as Edge System.
For more information on inbound data, data storage, API, and outbound data, see the following sections.

